posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'If you think it’s time to ditch the lawn mower, snow blower, and property taxes, we’ve got the answer!', 'The Grainwood Senior Apartments 55+ senior living apartment is an affordable housing community conveniently located in beautiful Prior Lake.', 'These gorgeous and hard-to-find one, two and three bedroom apartments features a spacious home that you’ll have plenty of room for an office and a guest room!', 'The open floor plans includes a large island kitchen with granite counters and informal seating for four, a king-size master bedroom with its own private bath, walk-in closets, a private balcony, and an in-home washer/dryer!', 'This is where luxury meets affordability!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Gorgeous Grounds Landscaping & Well-Maintained Community Spaces', '- Water, Sewer & Trash Removal Included', '- Large Bedrooms with Roomy Walk-In Closet(s)', '- High-Speed Internet & Cable Ready', '- Beautiful Community Room with Lounge Area & Cozy Fireplace', '- Dishwasher & Garbage Disposal', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Grainwood Senior Apartments is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community;
